Chief Executive Officer, RHF Ventures and RHF Guest House Resort in Abuja, Dr.Â  Amina Adetunji, has been elevated to the elite fellowship of the Nigeria Institute of Management (NIM). Mrs Adetunji, a Doctorate degree holder in Agricultural Economics, and a former senior manager with the Bank of Agriculture, will be inducted on Thursday in Abuja.  A consultant, business woman and a renowned philanthropist, Mrs Adetunji runs a foundation with her husband, Mr. Adediran Adetunji, Principal Partner, Diran Adetunji & Associates, an Estate Surveying and Valuation firm in Abuja. The foundation called Diran & Amina Foundation helps widows and orphans through scholarships and business grants. 